                                <note>Upper left corner: National Library book label with current signum.</note>
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <locus from="SL1r" to="SL1r" scheme="folios"/>
                                <note>Upper left corner, in ink by a modern hand: <quote>
                                        <del>Isl. 8o No 21.2.</del>
                                    </quote>; below: <quote>Fragment af legender.</quote>; below: <quote>
